    "Before proceeding with DEA, it is good practice to preprocess your data, e.g. to remove samples for which annotations are missing and exclude genes with very low levels of expression. This is not necessary in the case of our synthetic data, but don’t forget this step if you are using real data. To this end you can use the code below.\n",
